SDM class

SDM_class.Rd

This is the class for output from the fitting functions (gam_sdm, mlp_sdm, and brt_sdm). The SDM object is a list with the abundance and presence fits plus meta added from the OM object. This allows easy plotting from fitted SDMs. See OM for a description of the meta element.
